      "text": "**Self-host the powerful [Nari Labs Dia TTS models](https://github.com/nari-labs/dia) \u2014 including the original **Dia 1.6B** and the new **Dia 2** family (1B & 2B) \u2014 with this enhanced FastAPI server! Features hot-swappable model switching, an intuitive Web UI, flexible API endpo\u2026"
